ApproxsimClient.proj
Class MGRSConversion

java.lang.Object
  ApproxsimClient.proj.MGRSConversion

public class MGRSConversion
extends Object

This class implements the conversion between geodetic values (latitude and longitude) and MGRS coordinates.

getGridValues

public static ApproxsimClient.proj.ReducedUPSConstant getGridValues(long zone)
This method sets the letter range used for the 2nd letter in the MGRS coordinate string, based on the set number of the utm zone. It also sets the false northing using a value of A for the second letter of the grid square, based on the grid pattern and set number of the utm zone.

Parameters:
zone - zone number.
Returns:
2nd letter low number, 2nd letter high number and false northing.
